href=3D"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.uri(v=3Dvs.110).a=
spx">Uri</A>=20
instance without creating a new <A =
href=3D"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.uri(v=3Dvs.110).a=
spx">Uri</A>=20
instance for each modification.</P>
<P>The <SPAN class=3D"selflink">UriBuilder</SPAN> properties provide =
read/write=20
access to the read-only <A =
href=3D"https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/system.uri(v=3Dvs.110).a=
spx">Uri</A>=20
properties so that they can be modified.</P></DIV></DIV></DIV>
